    <section name="Boolean">
      <span class="shortdesc">What is a boolean?</span>

    <p>A boolean is a yes or no question. A boolean has a name,
     identifying the question, and a value, which is the answer to the
     question and which can only be yes or no (or true or false, which
     comes down to the same thing).
   </p>
